1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 26=

3
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:57,780
Yunqiu.

4
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:59,460
Yunqiu, are you alright?

5
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:03,220
I'll be fine once you're dead.

6
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:10,420
Yunqiu.

7
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:13,660
Did he force you to do something?

8
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:16,540
I didn't force her.

9
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:18,300
She brought it up herself.

10
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:21,020
Look at you now,
pathetic like a stray dog.

11
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:23,260
Who would still want someone like you?

12
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:25,140
Isn't that right?

13
00:01:29,860 --> 00:01:30,940
Impossible.

14
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:32,899
Impossible...

15
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,220
Nothing is impossible.

16
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,220
I saved you before

17
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,020
because I heard you'd
been appointed Commander.

18
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:40,779
I even gave you my address

19
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:41,940
so you could come marry me.

20
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:44,140
But now it seems

21
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:46,260
there's no chance for you to rise again.

22
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,340
Please stop dragging me down.

23
00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:49,620
Alright?

24
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:57,000
♪What is there to seek or desire,
trapped in worldly sorrow?♪

25
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:01,340
The lieutenant's aim is very accurate.

26
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,699
Better be careful when firing.

27
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:04,980
Yunqiu, don't listen to him.

28
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:07,140
There's only one bullet in the gun.

29
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:08,980
You only get one chance.

30
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,300
Gu Shaoyan.

31
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:12,900
What are you saying to her?

32
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:17,740
What are you saying to her?

33
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:20,500
Yunqiu.

34
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,460
Yunqiu, don't believe a word he says.

35
00:02:23,260 --> 00:02:24,580
Don't listen to him, Yunqiu!

36
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:29,000
♪Even fleeting happiness is enough♪

37
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,919
♪This heart and love slowly fade away♪

38
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:35,120
♪What kind of ending
will this fate bring?♪

39
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,599
♪Crossing through
the barriers of dreams♪

40
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:39,400
♪Burning away all my devotion♪

41
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,940
This is the jade pendant you gave me.

42
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,660
It once blocked a bullet for me.

43
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,940
I should put it on you too.

44
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,820
May it keep you safe as well.

45
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,099
(Shaoyuan,)

46
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:52,059
(there's no other choice now.)

47
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,860
(This is the only gamble left.)

48
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:57,140
(I just hope you'll be as lucky
as I once was.)

49
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:04,460
(If it can stop the bullet,)

50
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:07,340
(you'll fall into
a state of fake death,)

51
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,339
(and briefly stop breathing.)

52
00:03:09,340 --> 00:03:11,059
(If it works,)

53
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,780
(live on well.)

54
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:15,940
(We'll meet again in the next life.)

55
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:26,219
Since childhood,

56
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:28,219
he was always the one praised,

57
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,980
while I was the one blamed.

58
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,740
Never thought that today,

59
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:36,460
you'd finally get a taste
of being trampled underfoot.

60
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:41,399
♪This heart and love slowly fade away♪

61
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:44,219
♪What kind of ending
will this fate bring?♪

62
00:03:44,220 --> 00:03:45,579
You really killed him.

63
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,179
♪Crossing through
the barriers of dreams♪

64
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,979
You really killed Lu Shaoyuan.

65
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,580
My dear sister in law

66
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:53,580
killed her own husband.

67
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:57,140
You killed him
so you could be with me, didn't you?

68
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:59,460
For the sake of the dead,

69
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,700
could Xue Wan come collect his body?

70
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:05,100
She always said I stole her husband.

71
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,100
Now that he's dead,

72
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:08,620
I'll return him to her.

73
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,180
Xue Wan?

74
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,220
That foolish rich girl?

75
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:15,940
Fine.

76
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:17,500
I'd love to see

77
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:19,019
what kind of reaction she'll have

78
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:20,620
when she sees this.

79
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:24,139
Have Xue Wan come collect the body.

80
00:04:24,140 --> 00:04:24,780
Yes.

81
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:29,060
Zhuang Yunqiu!

82
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,620
Zhuang Yunqiu!

83
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:34,020
Wake up, Zhuang Yunqiu!

84
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:35,300
Zhuang Yunqiu!

85
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:36,860
Zhuang Yunqiu!

86
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:40,019
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

87
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:44,380
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

88
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:57,740
Madam is awake!

89
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:00,200
You've been unconscious
for over half a month.

90
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:02,620
If you're feeling any discomfort,
you must tell me right away.

91
00:05:02,980 --> 00:05:04,340
Go get the Commander.

92
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:05,140
Yes.

93
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,420
Wait.

94
00:05:06,540 --> 00:05:07,740
During these past two weeks,

95
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:10,220
have there been any updates
from the Xue family?

96
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:11,899
The day you collapsed,

97
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:14,900
many doctors were called to the Xue residence
for emergency treatment.

98
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:16,260
Was that person saved?

99
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,900
I'm not sure about that.

100
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,459
But I heard

101
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:22,360
those doctors treated him
for days without success.

102
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:25,300
Later, the Xue family sent people out
of town to bring back famous physicians.

103
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:27,460
They're still trying to save him.

104
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,300
That means there's still hope.

105
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:32,820
You're awake.

106
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:38,380
I've taken care of you for half a month,

107
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:40,460
yet you still wanted to kill me.

108
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:46,100
But I do have good news for you.

109
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:47,980
You're going to be a mother.

110
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:52,140
From now on, even if you
don't care about yourself,

111
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:55,060
you should think about the child.

112
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,100
What did you say?

113
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:09,140
Don't believe it?

114
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:11,060
Ask the doctor then.

115
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,420
Yes, Madam.

116
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,500
Your body is weak.

117
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:17,340
During this period, you must do everything
you can to protect the pregnancy.

118
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,180
Otherwise,

119
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:20,260
the child could be
in danger at any time.

120
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:25,020
You may leave.

121
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,460
Yes.

122
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:30,620
Did you hear what the doctor said?

123
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:34,460
Whether this child lives safely or not

124
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,620
depends on

125
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,060
your behavior.

126
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:10,620
Nianchi...

127
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:12,300
Nianchi...

128
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:14,780
You're awake.

129
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:17,900
Here.

130
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,620
Where am I?

131
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:25,780
This is my home.

132
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,420
Why am I here?

133
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:30,860
You were unconscious for three months.

134
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,220
I saved you.

135
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,660
Where's Zhuang Yunqiu?

136
00:07:35,380 --> 00:07:36,740
You're still asking about her?

137
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:38,259
She was the one who shot you.

138
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,420
Have you forgotten?

139
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:41,860
How is she now?

140
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:43,900
Her?

141
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:46,100
She's living quite comfortably now.

142
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:48,460
She's the Commander's wife now.

143
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:50,100
Commander Cheng's wife.

144
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,060
Don't believe it?

145
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,099
Look for yourself.

146
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,260
It's in the newspaper.

147
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:00,980
Look.

148
00:08:02,580 --> 00:08:05,660
(Cheng Yi and Zhuang Yunqiu
Wedding Announcement)

149
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:20,980
Nianchi,

150
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:23,020
pull yourself together, alright?

151
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,420
Miss Xue,

152
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:33,140
I'm not Gu Nianchi.

153
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:36,420
I know.

154
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:38,340
You two are twins.

155
00:08:40,180 --> 00:08:41,780
But whether you believe it or not,

156
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:44,580
our fate was tied together long ago.

157
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:47,020
You don't want to remain
a discarded pawn either, do you?

158
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:49,220
So pull yourself together.

159
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:51,220
Take back everything
that belongs to you.

160
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:54,300
Don't let those who care for you suffer
while your enemies celebrate.

161
00:08:58,260 --> 00:09:01,060
(Cheng Yi and Zhuang Yunqiu
Wedding Announcement)

162
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:20,510
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

163
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:27,140
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

164
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:31,220
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

165
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:34,570
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

166
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:39,860
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

167
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:46,170
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

168
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:52,830
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

169
00:09:53,370 --> 00:09:56,750
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

170
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,949
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

171
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:05,089
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

172
00:10:05,090 --> 00:10:09,409
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

173
00:10:09,410 --> 00:10:11,989
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

174
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:14,269
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

175
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:17,819
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

176
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:22,349
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

177
00:10:22,350 --> 00:10:24,880
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

178
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:26,969
♪Still I walk into♪

179
00:10:26,970 --> 00:10:30,569
♪The trap you set without regret♪

180
00:10:30,570 --> 00:10:34,619
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

181
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:37,199
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

182
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,359
♪A stand in can never cross♪

183
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:42,799
♪The shortest distance between us♪

184
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:47,770
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

185
00:10:47,930 --> 00:10:52,600
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

186
00:10:55,380 --> 00:10:56,949
♪A substitute♪

187
00:10:56,950 --> 00:11:01,950
♪Needs no reason♪

